sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client as Cliente HTTP
    participant Ctrl as TransactionsController
    participant Val as RegisterTransactionValidator<br/>[FluentValidation]
    participant Svc as TransactionService<br/>(Application Service — ADR-015)
    participant Dom as Transaction<br/>(Rich Domain)
    participant UoW as IUnitOfWork
    participant Repo as ITransactionRepository
    participant Outbox as IOutboxRepository<br/>(ADR-025)

    Client->>Ctrl: POST /api/v1/transactions<br/>body = [{...}, {...}, ...]<br/>(HTTPS/JSON, sempre array)

    Note over Ctrl,Val: Validation manual item-a-item<br/>(param é List<T>, não dispara auto-validation)
    loop for each request in array
        Ctrl->>Val: ValidateAsync(request[i])
    end

    alt qualquer item inválido
        Val-->>Ctrl: ValidationResult.Errors<br/>(keyed por [i].PropertyName)
        Ctrl-->>Client: 400 Bad Request<br/>ValidationProblemDetails
    else todos válidos
        Ctrl->>Svc: RegisterManyAsync(requests)

        loop for each request
            Svc->>Dom: Transaction.Register(amount, type, ...)
            Note over Dom: Money.From(amount)<br/>MovementDate.From(date)<br/>valida invariantes
        end

        alt DomainException em algum item
            Dom-->>Svc: throw DomainException
            Svc-->>Ctrl: throw (nada persistido ainda)
            Ctrl-->>Client: 422 Unprocessable Entity
        else todos os Transaction criados
            Svc->>UoW: BeginAsync()

            loop for each transaction (mesma UoW)
                Svc->>Repo: InsertAsync(transaction)
                Svc->>Outbox: EnqueueAsync(EventId, "TransactionRegistered", JSON payload)
                Note over Svc,Outbox: INSERT transação + outbox<br/>na MESMA tx — atomicidade<br/>fecha janela do ADR-007
            end

            Svc->>UoW: CommitAsync()
            Svc-->>Ctrl: IReadOnlyList<TransactionResponse>
            Ctrl-->>Client: 201 Created<br/>(array de responses na mesma ordem)
        end
    end

    Note over Outbox: Publicação assíncrona pelo<br/>OutboxDispatcher BackgroundService —<br/>ver "fluxo-outbox-dispatch.mmd"
